OL,3,CSir Ian McKellen: Fat suit saved me
OL,4,Cfrom worse injuries after West End fall
OL,6,FSir Ian McKellen has revealed that a
OL,7,Ffat suit "saved" his "ribs and other
OL,8,Fjoints" during a fall from a stage in
OL,9,Fthe West End but said he was "nervous"
OL,10,Fto leave his house after the accident.
OL,12,FThe veteran screen and stage actor,
OL,13,F85, lost his footing during a Player
OL,14,FKings fight scene in June when the
OL,15,Fproduction was at the Noel Coward
OL,16,FTheatre and has since been suffering
OL,17,Ffrom wrist and neck injuries.
OL,19,FSpeaking to Saga magazine, he said:
OL,20,F"I've relived that fall I don't know
OL,21,Fhow many times. It was horrible.
