OL,3,CSir Ian McKellen: Fat suit saved me
OL,4,Cfrom worse injuries after West End fall
OL,6,F"It was in the battle scene. My foot
OL,7,Fgot caught in a chair, and trying to
OL,8,Fshake it off I started to slide on
OL,9,Fsome newspaper that was scattered over
OL,10,Fthe stage, like I was on a skateboard.
OL,12,F"The more I tried to get rid of it,
OL,13,Fthe faster I proceeded down a step,
OL,14,Fonto the forestage, and then on to the
OL,15,Flap of someone in the front row.
OL,17,F"I started screaming, 'Help me!' and
OL,18,Fthen 'I'm sorry! I don't do this!'.
OL,19,FExtraordinary things. I thought it was
OL,20,Fthe end of something. It was very
OL,21,Fupsetting."
