OL,3,CSir Ian McKellen: Fat suit saved me
OL,4,Cfrom worse injuries after West End fall
OL,6,F"The end", he clarifies, did not mean
OL,7,F"my death. It was my participation in
OL,8,Fthe play. I have to keep assuring
OL,9,Fmyself that I'm not too old to act and
OL,10,Fit was just a bloody accident.
OL,12,F"I didn't lose consciousness, I hadn't
OL,13,Fbeen dizzy, but I've not been able to
OL,14,Fgo back and they still played without
OL,15,Fme.
OL,17,F"I don't feel guilty, but the accident
OL,18,Fhas let down the whole production," he
OL,19,Fsaid.
