OL,3,CSir Ian McKellen: Fat suit saved me
OL,4,Cfrom worse injuries after West End fall
OL,6,F"I feel such shame. I was hoping to be
OL,7,Fable to rejoin the play on the tour,
OL,8,Fbut I couldn't", he added.
OL,10,FSpeaking about his injuries he said:
OL,11,F"My chipped vertebrae and fractured
OL,12,Fwrist are not yet mended.
OL,14,F"I don't go out because I get nervous
OL,15,Fin case someone bangs into me, and
OL,16,FI've got agonising pains in my
OL,17,Fshoulders to do with my whole frame
OL,18,Fhaving been jolted.
