OL,3,CSir Ian McKellen: Fat suit saved me
OL,4,Cfrom worse injuries after West End fall
OL,6,FThe Lord Of The Rings actor said he is
OL,7,Fbeing looked after by his neighbours
OL,8,Fand joked that what he is missing the
OL,9,Fmost at the moment is the pub quiz at
OL,10,FThe Grapes, the pub he part-owns in
OL,11,Feast London.
OL,13,FSir Ian's understudy, David Semark,
OL,14,Fstepped in to finish the run in the
OL,15,FWest End and continued to play the
OL,16,Frole during the national tour.
OL,18,FSir Ian was unable to return due to
OL,19,Fhis injuries and told Saga magazine
OL,20,Fthat "there are suggestions we'll do
OL,21,F(the play) again, but we'll see".
